TopicTitle: Titan II GLV (With Gemini Capsule) Rocket Recreation

Articles.Content:
My first post ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif) ,now on topic, I recently made this rocket design by using the Gemini Capsule addon ([http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=6024.0](http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=6024.0)) and Novapunch Remix fuel tanks and liquid engines ([http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=4180.0](http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=4180.0)) which I retextured, I hope you like it, if you want to reply with any ideas on how I can improve feel free, I still have not finished the textures yet so I will add more detail in the future.
